vulnerabilities.title: Cross-site Scripting in Bootstrap-3-Typeahead
vulnerabilities.description: Bootstrap-3-Typeahead after version 4.0.2 is vulnerable to a cross-site scripting flaw in the highlighter() function. An attacker could exploit this via user interaction to execute code in the user's browser. This issue was introduced in commit `dbd1af5bf` and has not been fixed.
